text: "Pump It Up" is a 1978 song by Elvis Costello and the Attractions. It is the second single from his second studio album This Year's Model. It went to number 55 in Australia and number 24 in the United Kingdom. It went on to feature on several compilation albums and was used by Australian band Rogue Traders 2005 single Voodoo Child. ==Notes== ==References== Category:1978 songs Category:Elvis Costello songs
title: Pump It Up (Elvis Costello song)
